{"tid":1739910,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"西灣河/筲箕灣出現大陸人呃飯黨","createTime":"2019-11-19T19:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T19:18:41.000Z","uid":114264,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d3a08f3041ac7f839b28902bf0b03d6e4ea1404f","tid":1739910,"uid":114264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T19:00:32.000Z","msg":"話說星期日夜晚係西灣河行去筲箕灣<br />\n<br />\n首先遇到個男人講普通話「美女，美女，有事要你幫幫忙」，我一個人唔想理佢就扮聽唔到急步走<br />\n<br />\n行到筲箕灣南記門口有一男一女又係講普通話，諗住照行過唔理，但個男人拍我膀頭！頂佢個肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟住男人話「可以幫幫忙買外帶給我們食嗎？」我問「為什麼？」男人話「我們遇到麻煩」我話「不要」轉身即走，兩條友著得身光頸靚過我，女人又化晒妝！<br />\n<br />\n祖國唔係好有錢咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />身上冇現金又點？你地用先進科技we7pay囉！！或者支撚寶囉！！5分鐘後我行到去東大街又遇到兩條友，仆街男人又拍我膀頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />話「買個麵包也可以」痴撚線！！！！我應都唔應即走，屌你！你呃飯食到交下戲做功夫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇街坊遇過？？"},{"pid":"05c10ebfac207deb760555db2205951c34761ee8","tid":1739910,"uid":201414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T19:02:27.000Z","msg":"想問樓主訓左幾奈 呃飯黨都唔係咩新鮮事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dadb10fbec372b13fd8a0135afc3df9152367e78","tid":1739910,"uid":114264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05c10ebfac207deb760555db2205951c34761ee8","tid":1739910,"uid":201414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T19:02:27.000Z","msg":"想問樓主訓左幾奈 呃飯黨都唔係咩新鮮事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T19:07:27.000Z","msg":"我遇過幾個本地呀婆呃飯食（中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），但大陸人仲要同一晚發生就第一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7edfdca26ad1744068349f8fac7c7db9df277ef","tid":1739910,"uid":292119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05c10eb